Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.34,0:00:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃閃發光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦誒 你在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.89,0:00:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以去那邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.57,0:00:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生最近掉毛很嚴重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛會黏到衣服上的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啊 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.07,0:00:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫌我麻煩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.55,0:00:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你稍微出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.53,0:02:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看看 正合身！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那是因為按你的尺寸做的 自然合身啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.16,0:02:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 挺適合你的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那方面 不是那方面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來… 像普通的… 女孩子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 看起來跟外面的小姑娘一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生～！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:02:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真喜歡你～！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.47,0:02:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生～！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:02:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡你了～！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.93,0:03:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 黏到毛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底想怎樣啊 你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校哦 學校！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會交到朋友的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驢唇不對馬嘴啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.19,0:03:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}「對啦 名乃」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.61,0:03:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}「放學回去時要不要去吃冰淇淋？」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.03,0:03:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}「啊 誒 去啊 去啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}「那之後要去唱卡拉OK麼？」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}「誒？ 誒…」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}「但是 我…」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.29,0:03:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}「從來沒去過！」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}「我會教給你噠～」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}「大家一起去嘛～」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}「啊… 好… 好的」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}「那麼…」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之類的對話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.47,0:03:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}啊 博士！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.51,0:03:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看看 博士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣啊？ 適合我麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！好漂亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.15,0:03:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件睡衣 也很適合博士哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 超漂亮的～！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是跟平時一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.91,0:03:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本～～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本也超帥的～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\}你也來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手帕沒問題！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.83,0:04:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生證沒問題！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教科書沒問題！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筆記本沒問題！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鉛筆盒沒問題！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自動鉛筆沒問題！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自動鉛筆芯沒問題！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！沒有落下東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗噗噗～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有落下的東西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？誒 什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了的話…？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SNICKERS！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士～！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廚房裡準備好早飯和午飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請記得吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 洗好的衣服 等我回來了再拿進來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼都不用做就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 學校什麼時間結束啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三點半左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.04,0:04:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來的時候還要買晚飯的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到家大概五點鐘吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五點…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前沒說過的麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五點 那都晚上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.47,0:05:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對… 但是這是學校嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我走…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.39,0:05:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不想讓你去！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 剛才不還說可以去的嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以去！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}不可以 名乃 不可以去！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣… 都要遲到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把包還給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}滾啊滾×N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦誒 小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要那麼無理取鬧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 要不這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚飯做博士最喜歡的蛋包飯！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上回來的時候給你買鯊魚蛋糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.01,0:05:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒… 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再加上草莓果汁！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾啊滾×N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.85,0:05:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芥川獎也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可辦不到啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\c&HDECDA2&\pos(598,107)}雞蛋豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一時都不知道該怎麼辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.07,0:06:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸虧博士總算是讓步了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來我也能邁出做普通人的第一步…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘得乾乾淨淨啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背上的發條…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.13,0:06:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥氣的東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～的 大幹一場吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！ 幹勁滿滿的前輩！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想了好久… 也想不出答案
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果就來到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 現在給大家介紹轉校生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.95,0:06:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東雲同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.62,0:06:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果… 果然大家都很在意發條…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東雲同學 請自己寫下名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發條 非常顯眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不做點什麼矇混過去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 我… 我叫東雲名乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個聽我說啊 那個… 這個發條啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.99,0:07:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 那個… 實際上…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在來的途中被插上去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.54,0:07:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷場啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 哎呀 那個聽我說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是 其實吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是騙你們的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.63,0:07:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在解釋些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.55,0:07:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃啊 怎麼辦啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 就是說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不是像拇指是USB之類的 那種機器人似的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不行啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:03.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,520)\pos(800,360)}占\N卜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希～望明天～是個好～天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 關口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要光在看書 一起玩吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:16.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\pos(691,384)}圍\N棋\N足\N球\N部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易買來了人生遊戲的啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:19.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1020,0)\bord1\shad2\fnsimhei\fs40\c&HF2F2F2&\3c&H7A818A&\4c&H525D6C&\pos(328,60)}圍棋足球部  部長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.08,0:08:19.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimhei\fs45\bord1\shad2\frz314.985\pos(99,613)\c&H6269E0&\3c&HECEAE9&}人\N生\N游\N戲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:23.25,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1020,0)\bord1\shad2\fnsimhei\fs40\c&HF2F2F2&\3c&H7A818A&\4c&H525D6C&\pos(947,60)}圍棋足球部  部員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:23.25,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1020,0)\bord1\shad2\fnsimhei\fs36\3c&H7A818A&\4c&H525D6C&\pos(947,155)\c&HF1FCF8&}關口尤利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛～ 真無聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在圍棋足球部才能玩珍瓏棋局啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.93,0:08:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說我不會玩圍棋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了——
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是圍棋足球部吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.19,0:08:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要入部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級歡迎啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同學 你叫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.45,0:08:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一年級的櫻井誠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是二年級的部長 大工健三郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是一年級的關口君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 嘛 坐吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.63,0:09:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 怎麼玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩人生遊戲麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不進行練習麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圍棋足球的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.45,0:09:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實圍棋足球這個名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我創造的傳說中的社團活動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種競技實際上並不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上 就是大家在一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 說起來就是娛樂部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中的時候參加圍棋足球部了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前一直不知道這個學校有圍棋足球部來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 前段時間校舍上不是懸掛標語了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\bord0\shad0\fad(600,0)\c&H41403E&\pos(310,506)}目\N標\N日\N本\N第\N一\N！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才注意到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中學的時候是MVP來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:09:58.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,520)\shad2\pos(1150,360)\4c&HC2C1BE&}在\N意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東… 東雲同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 到！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是非常在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 後背的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這… 這…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.85,0:10:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 啊… 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.45,0:10:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 那個… 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}哎呀… 那個… 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.37,0:10:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的圍棋足球部 在做些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔—— 口頭說明的話有些困難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那給你來段個人表演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是顛球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.01,0:10:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從顛球…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從棋子…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單人德式拱橋摔！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此乃雪崩棋譜 三連星是也！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼情況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來隨隨便便創了一個部…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.41,0:11:00.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\pos(691,384)}圍\N棋\N足\N球\N部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:10:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得超有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:06.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,520)\shad1\pos(200,360)\4c&HC2C1BE&}鞋\N子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說… 等一下啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這突然是 怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裡啊 帕蒂？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(652,493)\c&H0A0A0A&\shad0\bord0\K100}隻{\K100}言{\K100}片{\K100}語
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本～～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}阪本×N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.28,0:11:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 我說… 住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是問我怎麼回事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不停的轉來轉去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:55.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,520)\bord2\blur3\pos(100,360)\4c&HC2C1BE&}帕\N蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才第一天就出那麼大的差錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.74,0:12:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在懷疑我是怪小孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 名乃你帶便當來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.01,0:12:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 啊… 是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是帶便當吃的麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很普通的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:13:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很… 很漂亮… 呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了啊 小祐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午休這都快結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 回來的時候 被車和狗把鞋子搶走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,費了好大勁去追
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然聽不出來是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.51,0:13:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之貌似是件大事啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 但是平安無事的拿到便當比什麼都強
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？ 小祐你的午飯呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邊走邊吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.19,0:13:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？吃什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.98,0:13:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回鍋肉便當
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好牛！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回鍋…什麼的 嘛 算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 名乃 要來這邊一起吃麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於名乃的事情多講給我聽聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有認為我是普通的女孩子啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難… 難道說… 想要做朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 名乃背後的那個是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:13:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這… 這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不是什麼可疑的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.01,0:14:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.47,0:14:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}難道說名乃是機器人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 說什麼蠢話呢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉啊 小祐很笨的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.77,0:14:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要沒時間了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要趕快吃完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 小祐 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.80,0:14:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒青花魚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓你給我帶的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是燒青花魚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炒麵啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs34}譯註：燒青花魚{\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7\fs30}（焼きさば）{\r\fs34}、炒麵{\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7\fs30}（焼きそば）{\r\fs34}音很近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.23,0:14:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說… 聽錯了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.61,0:14:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歉抱歉抱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:14:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是裝裝可愛就能解決的問題哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是特別的問題哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼？ 這很接近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看只有一個字的差別嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.74,0:15:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是夠了 只能這樣了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 米飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白米飯啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…雖說是這麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一個菜我怎麼吃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.76,0:15:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 因為美緒你自己說的燒青花魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炒麵啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炒過的 麵條 啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你看 這種事件 寫到博客裡面作為笑點給大家看的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有電腦哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不要這麼怒髮衝冠啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦 現在再給你去買吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿錢來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥我還要給你錢啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.91,0:15:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我沒有錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了的話趕緊給我買回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午休就要結束了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK OK
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩 這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩了一個比索啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前想著留下來作為紀念
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.43,0:16:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩阿根廷比索了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩阿根廷 比索了啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿根廷 比索！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說明明是小祐出錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.48,0:16:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該小祐你出錢啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.98,0:16:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了 我剛才買了自己的便當 沒有錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那—— 我的午飯怎麼辦啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.32,0:16:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不 吃青花魚！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青你妹——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}青花魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說之前小祐你就很令人煩躁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次每次都抄別人的作業啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己稍微做一做會怎樣啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個笨蛋！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個笨蛋跟美緒吃不了午飯是不是完全沒關？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全有關係喲！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥關係？ 說出來看看哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.88,0:16:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是個笨蛋 所以聽錯了對吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 聽錯這種程度的事誰都會有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這事唧唧歪歪唧唧歪歪 你心眼太小了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.73,0:17:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早飯也沒吃 事關生死哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正笨蛋是不能理解吶！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是笨蛋！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.11,0:17:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你都承認你是笨蛋了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事先說明啊 這{\fsp8}次{\b1\fs54\bord2\shad2}絕對{\fs48\b0\bord3\shad3}{\fsp0}不會借你作業了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 不用 不用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒你忘了我也不會借給你抄的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要看你那破作業喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說你都給我買錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連一個道歉也沒有麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我下跪道歉啊！下跪！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下跪道歉就可以了吧 下跪道歉！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 真是非常對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看！ 我道歉了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就可以了吧？ 這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？！ 那根本不是下跪吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 對哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是下跪哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是身體前傾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前·傾！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥不給我下跪哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.27,0:17:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為姐怒了喲！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.24,0:17:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 美緒才是笨蛋吧！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊那是 之前的那個 奇怪的插畫啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 奇怪的插畫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:17:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢…蠢啊你！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 那些插畫？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙啊 莫名其妙啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我畫的易懂點啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還眼鏡呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢啊你！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢啊你！ 蠢啊你！ 蠢啊你！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.34,0:18:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫個白癡似的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才蠢吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊給我吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.81,0:18:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你點的這個燒青花魚！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我點的是炒麵！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我下跪道歉！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭深深的低下去！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.48,0:18:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經買了的東西 沒有辦法了吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我身為人類的道歉啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.07,0:18:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個人渣！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.28,0:18:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓你見識見識 真正的下跪吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是… 真正的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下跪道歉啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還少一句「買成燒青花魚了真是抱歉」呢！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你下跪謝罪對吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 說啊你！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說「買成燒青花魚了真是抱歉」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 趕緊說吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說「我是個笨蛋真是對不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠心道歉啊 你這個人渣！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.18,0:18:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 趕緊的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點說！ 笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:18:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊道歉 白癡！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渣滓！ 白癡！ 笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.16,0:19:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 一直說笨蛋笨蛋的 美緒你好吵啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.83,0:19:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你交往了半年了 你瞭解我些什麼啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是 哪裡懂我的畫啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.71,0:19:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫得那麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.09,0:19:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去做漫畫家多好！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說… 說什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.47,0:19:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟個笨蛋似的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說別人笨蛋的人才是笨蛋吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己在說笨蛋吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒說喲！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.81,0:19:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你的那種特質 我倒也不討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈… 哈！？ 說什麼呢！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦子明明很好！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真… 真囉嗦吶 你個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑臉的天才！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什… 什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,0:20:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是！ 虧你畫畫那麼好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真囉嗦！ 虧你跑得那麼快！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧你腦子那麼好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧你那麼樂觀！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧你腦子那麼好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是 虧你腦子那麼好！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.71,0:20:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\bord0\shad0\c&H8C928E&\pos(670,245)}圍棋！！足球部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\bord0\shad0\c&H8C928E&\pos(901,537)}那\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\bord0\shad0\c&H8C928E&\pos(851,609)}棋\N子\N和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\bord0\shad0\c&H8C928E&\pos(803,627)}足\N球\N的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\bord0\shad0\c&H8C928E&\pos(752,611)}故\N事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}前輩！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\c&H7F8387&\fs40\fad(680,680)\bord0\shad0\pos(442,236)}黑與白的\N魂！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.62,0:20:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我… 好不甘！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你還有明年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一定！前輩的份也一起加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}太好啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的事情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.09,0:21:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶 名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上學有趣麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了好多事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說吶？怎麼說吶？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.31,0:21:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友啊 真的好贊啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.32,0:21:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真贊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.57,0:21:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 我說 莫名其妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了！怎麼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.04,0:21:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.87,0:21:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請幫我把後背的發條拿下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.88,0:21:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校的生活會有各種各樣的情況…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是 被人懷疑是機器人來的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.39,0:21:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話就交不到朋友了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能交到哦 因為很可愛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不可愛呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛哦 發條
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣都好啦 趕緊做飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士～！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.16,0:23:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是足球…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.95,0:23:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢啊踢啊 被各種踢 踢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢啊 踢壞了 踢到死
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.79,0:23:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就長眠了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.12,0:23:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話日常是第十五話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.92,0:23:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.68,0:22:14.78,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}いま私の願いごとが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.69,0:22:25.95,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}かなうならば　翼がほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.31,0:22:34.88,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)\blur3}この背中の　鳥のように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.26,0:22:48.31,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}白い翼つけてください
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.94,0:22:53.94,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}この大空に　翼をひろげ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.11,0:22:58.82,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}飛んで行きたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.28,0:23:04.24,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}悲しみのない　自由な空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.41,0:23:12.21,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}翼はためかせ　行きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.68,0:22:14.78,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}如今對我來講心中所願所想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.69,0:22:25.95,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}能夠實現的話 真想要一雙翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.31,0:22:34.88,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)\blur3}在我的後背上 像那鳥兒一樣
